  {
    id: 'ch10', num: 10, status: 'done',
    title: 'Nonlinear and Long Memory Models',
    titleZh: '非线性与长记忆模型',
    pages: 'p413-456',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch10-nonlinear/',
    sections: [
      { id: '10.1', title: 'ARCH/GARCH 条件异方差', note: String.raw`ARCH(s)：$h_t = \omega_0 + \sum \omega_i a_{t-i}^2$\nGARCH(s,r)：加入 $\sum \beta_i h_{t-i}$\n\n$a_t$ 零均值不相关但不独立——通过条件方差关联\n波动率聚集：大波动后跟大波动` },
      { id: '10.2-3', title: '非线性 + 长记忆', note: String.raw`TAR（门限 AR）：不同区制用不同 AR → 极限环\n双线性模型：$z_{t-i}$ 与 $a_{t-j}$ 的交互\n\nARFIMA：分数差分 $(1-B)^d$，$d \in (-0.5, 0.5)$\n$0 < d < 0.5$：长记忆，ACF 幂律衰减` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch11', num: 11, status: 'done',
    title: 'Transfer Function Models',
    titleZh: '转换函数模型',
    pages: 'p439-500',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch11-15-advanced/',
    sections: [
      { id: '11.1', title: '离散传递函数', note: String.raw`$Y_t = v(B)X_t + N_t = \frac{\omega(B)}{\delta(B)}B^b X_t + N_t$\n\n$v_j$：脉冲响应函数\n$b$：纯滞后\n稳定性：$\delta(B)=0$ 根在圆外` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch12', num: 12, status: 'done',
    title: 'Transfer Function Model Building',
    titleZh: '转换函数模型的建立',
    pages: 'p501-564',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch11-15-advanced/',
    sections: [
      { id: '12.1-3', title: '预白化 + CCF 识别', note: String.raw`预白化输入 → 交叉相关函数 CCF → 估计脉冲响应\n从 CCF 模式判断 $b, s, r$ → 有理传递函数\n联合 MLE 估计传递函数 + 噪声模型` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch13', num: 13, status: 'done',
    title: 'Intervention Analysis and Outlier Detection',
    titleZh: '干扰分析与异常值检测',
    pages: 'p565-603',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch11-15-advanced/',
    sections: [
      { id: '13.1-2', title: '干预变量 + 异常值', note: String.raw`干预变量：阶跃（Step）$S_t^{(T)}$ 和脉冲（Pulse）$P_t^{(T)}$\n$Y_t = \frac{\omega(B)}{\delta(B)}B^b \xi_t + N_t$\n\n异常值：AO（附加）vs IO（创新）\nChen & Liu 迭代检测算法` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch14', num: 14, status: 'done',
    title: 'Multivariate Time Series Analysis',
    titleZh: '多元时间序列分析',
    pages: 'p605-674',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch11-15-advanced/',
    sections: [
      { id: '14.1-3', title: 'VAR + Granger 因果 + 协整', note: String.raw`VAR(p)：$\mathbf{z}_t = \sum \Phi_i \mathbf{z}_{t-i} + \mathbf{a}_t$\nGranger 因果：$X$ 的过去值有助于预测 $Y$？\n协整：非平稳序列的线性组合平稳 → VECM\n\n多站点光伏预测 = 多变量时序问题` },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 'ch15', num: 15, status: 'done',
    title: 'Aspects of Process Control',
    titleZh: '过程控制',
    pages: 'p675-717',
    blogUrl: '/blog/2026-03-16-box-ch11-15-advanced/',
    sections: [
      { id: '15.1-3', title: '反馈控制与最小方差', note: String.raw`反馈控制：$X_t = g(e_t, e_{t-1}, \ldots)$\n最小方差控制：输出方差最小化\nBox-Jenkins 方法：先建模再设计控制器 > 盲调 PID\n\n应用：储能调度、逆变器功率控制` },
    ],
  },
];

const done = chapters.filter(c => c.status === 'done').length;
const total = chapters.length;
const pct = Math.round(done / total * 100);
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
  <BaseHead title="Box 时间序列分析精读笔记 | Python Ship" description="Box, Jenkins & Reinsel《Time Series Analysis: Forecasting and Control》精读笔记——ARIMA、转换函数、干扰分析、多元时序、离散控制" />
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/katex/katex.min.css" />
  <style>
    .book-container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .book-hero { text-align: center; padding: 2rem 0 1rem; }
    .book-hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a78bfa, #c084fc); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; margin-bottom: .3rem; }
    .book-hero .subtitle { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .book-hero .author { color: #64748b; font-size: .9rem; margin-top: .4rem; }
    .progress-section { margin: 1.2rem 0; text-align: center; }
    .progress-bar { width: 100%; height: 8px; background: #2a2d3e; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden; margin: .5rem 0; }
    .progress-fill { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #a78bfa, #c084fc); border-radius: 4px; transition: width .4s; }
    .progress-text { font-size: .85rem; color: #94a3b8; }
    .ch-card { background: #1a1d2e; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 1rem; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #2a2d3e; }
    .ch-card.done { border-left: 3px solid #4ade80; }
    .ch-card.pending { border-left: 3px solid #334155; opacity: .55; }
    .ch-header { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: .8rem 1rem; cursor: pointer; gap: .8rem; user-select: none; }
    .ch-header:hover { background: #222640; }
    .ch-num { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #a78bfa; min-width: 2.2rem; }
    .ch-info { flex: 1; }
    .ch-title-zh { font-weight: 700; color: #f1f5f9; }
    .ch-title-en { font-size: .82rem; color: #64748b; font-style: italic; }
    .ch-meta { display: flex; gap: .6rem; align-items: center; }
    .ch-pages { font-size: .78rem; color: #475569; }
    .ch-badge { font-size: .72rem; padding: .12rem .45rem; border-radius: 4px; }
    .ch-badge.done { background: #166534; color: #4ade80; }
    .ch-badge.pending { background: #1e1e2e; color: #475569; }
    .ch-toggle { font-size: .85rem; color: #64748b; transition: transform .2s; }
    .ch-card.open .ch-toggle { transform: rotate(90deg); }
    .ch-body { display: none; padding: 0 1rem 1rem; }
    .ch-card.open .ch-body { display: block; }
    .blog-link { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: .8rem; font-size: .85rem; color: #4ade80; text-decoration: none; }
    .blog-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .section { margin-bottom: .8rem; }
    .section-id { color: #a78bfa; font-weight: 700; font-size: .85rem; margin-right: .4rem; }
    .section-title { color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; font-size: .95rem; cursor: pointer; }
    .section-title:hover { color: #a78bfa; }
    .note { display: none; background: #13152a; border-radius: 6px; padding: .8rem 1rem; margin-top: .4rem; font-size: .88rem; color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.7; white-space: pre-wrap; }
    .section.open .note { display: block; }
    .back-link { display: inline-block; margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #a78bfa; text-decoration: none; font-size: .9rem; }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <div class="book-container">
      <div class="book-hero">
        <h1>📈 Time Series Analysis: Forecasting and Control</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">时间序列分析：预测与控制</div>
        <div class="author">George E.P. Box, G.M. Jenkins, G.C. Reinsel · Wiley, 4th Ed. (2008) · 765p · 15 章</div>
      </div>
      <div class="progress-section">
        <div class="progress-bar">
          <div class="progress-fill" style={`width: ${pct}%`}></div>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-text">{done}/{total} 章完成 ({pct}%)</div>
      </div>

      {chapters.map(ch => (
        <div class={`ch-card ${ch.status}`} id={ch.id}>
          <div class="ch-header" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
            <span class="ch-num">{ch.num}</span>
            <div class="ch-info">
              <div class="ch-title-zh">{ch.titleZh}</div>
              <div class="ch-title-en">{ch.title}</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ch-meta">
              {ch.pages && <span class="ch-pages">{ch.pages}</span>}
              <span class={`ch-badge ${ch.status}`}>{ch.status === 'done' ? '✅' : '⏳'}</span>
              {ch.sections.length > 0 && <span class="ch-toggle">▶</span>}
            </div>
          </div>
          {ch.sections.length > 0 && (
            <div class="ch-body">
              {ch.blogUrl && <a href={ch.blogUrl} class="blog-link">📝 感悟博客 →</a>}
              {ch.sections.map(sec => (
                <div class="section">
                  <div onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    <span class="section-id">{sec.id}</span>
                    <span class="section-title">{sec.title}</span>
                  </div>
                  {sec.note && <div class="note" set:html={sec.note.replace(/\\n/g, '<br/>')} />}
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          )}
        </div>
      ))}

      <div style="margin-top: 2rem; padding: 1rem; background: #1a1d2e; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 3px solid #a78bfa;">
        <a href="/blog/box-timeseries-thinking/" style="color: #a78bfa; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;">🧠 思维训练 — Box 时间序列逻辑串联 →</a>
        <div style="color: #94a3b8; font-size: .85rem; margin-top: .3rem;">推理链、跨教材知识网络、已解决的困惑</div>
      </div>

      <a href="/textbook/" class="back-link">← 返回教材目录</a>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
  <script src="/katex/katex.min.js" defer></script>
  <script src="/katex/auto-render.min.js" defer></script>
  <script is:inline>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
      if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
        renderMathInElement(document.body, {
          delimiters: [
            { left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true },
            { left: '$', right: '$', display: false },
          ],
        });
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
